item.title: My rsps online need help
item.dc:creator: @Hugh_Jass Hugh Jass
item.description:
@Hugh_Jass wrote:

You’re starting your server with the local IP… If you’re trying to get players, you need to make sure you port forwarded and replace all the “127.0.0.1” Local Ip addresses to your No-IP. Ex. “Examplescape.no-ip.biz”
If you need help Port Forwarding Go to “www.portforward.com”. It gives a complete guide, depending on your router, to portforward for an RSPS. Hope I helped.
